    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_7_476-510",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "476-510",
      "markText": "这两份自撰墓志铭的意义在于，它们冲击了人们以为自传更为真实可靠的想法",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=476&rangeEnd=510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=476&rangeEnd=510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_3_1802-1844",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1802-1844",
      "markText": "早夭的孩子很少出现在家谱或父母的传记中，但他们却是墓志中被父母和家人殷切怀念的对象。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1802&rangeEnd=1844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1802&rangeEnd=1844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_3_6492-6531",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6492-6531",
      "markText": "孝文帝（467—499年在位）的汉化政策之一就是下令将军中的死者安葬在洛阳邙山",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6492&rangeEnd=6531",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6492&rangeEnd=6531"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_6_3969-4168",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3969-4168",
      "markText": "幽监寂寂，天道芒芒。生浮命促，昼短宵长。一归细柳，不反扶桑。霜凝青，风悲白杨。蕙卧兰畹，无绝芬芳。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3969&rangeEnd=4168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3969&rangeEnd=4168"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_3_1055-1093",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1055-1093",
      "markText": "从宋代起，作为官府与士绅密切合作产物的地方志，收录了越来越多的地方名人传记。",
      "totalCount": 55,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1055&rangeEnd=1093",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1055&rangeEnd=1093"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_3_5658-5696",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5658-5696",
      "markText": "至今出土的西汉墓志不到二十方，显然，墓志出现之前的种种志墓方法仍然在被使用。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5658&rangeEnd=5696",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5658&rangeEnd=5696"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_3_7049-7079",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7049-7079",
      "markText": "宋代的墓志铭更甚，五千字以上的并不罕见，有的甚至接近一万字。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7049&rangeEnd=7079",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7049&rangeEnd=7079"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_3_10026-10072",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "10026-10072",
      "markText": "这些已经功成名就的文人宁愿请求好友或同僚为自己的父母歌功颂德，并借机由他们赞誉求志者的孝行。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10026&rangeEnd=10072",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10026&rangeEnd=10072"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063891_5_1864-1892",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1864-1892",
      "markText": "司马楚之陪同父亲的遗体前往东晋首都建康附近的丹阳进行埋葬",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063891&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1864&rangeEnd=1892",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e632150813ab7f75g0119c1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1864&rangeEnd=1892"
    },
